WEBVTT

00:04:00.029 --> 00:04:02.163
and give it to others.

00:04:03.173 --> 00:04:04.863
But something was still bugging me,

00:04:04.887 --> 00:04:06.902
something was still
keeping me up at night.

00:04:09.038 --> 00:04:10.905
What about those people

00:04:11.783 --> 00:04:16.591
who have genuinely no control
over where they live?

00:04:17.704 --> 00:04:21.848
Every hour -- in the space
of your intermission --

00:04:21.872 --> 00:04:26.152
4,000 new homes are needed in the world.

00:04:26.506 --> 00:04:28.362
Wrap your head around that number.

00:04:29.585 --> 00:04:36.385
That's an astonishing 35 million homes
globally, every year.